  "title": "Motherhood the Musical",
  "description": "Having a baby is just the beginning...motherhood is for life! It's climbing a mountain to find out that there is laundry on top. This high energy musical comedy will transport you through some of motherhood's most sentimental and laugh out loud moments. Come relive them all from hilarious to heart warming!",
  "credits": "<strong>Playwright</strong>: Sue Fabisch<br/><strong>Director</strong>: Jane Gusdal-Director and Choreographer<br/><strong>Cast</strong>: Jane Gusdal, Pam Sherman, Kate Down, April McCorquindale, Veronica Dennis<br/><strong>Designers</strong>: Streberg Photography &amp; Film, Kyra Thompson<br/><strong>Stage Manager</strong>: Rob Nichols<br/>",
  "website": "",
  "plain_language": "This funny musical comedy follows three moms sharing honest, and often hilarious, advice and perspectives to their nervous first-time mom friend at her surprise baby shower.",
